# Momentum Habit Tracker — Environment Variables
#
# This app is a pure client-side SPA with no backend.
# All data persists to browser localStorage — no server or database required.
#
# No environment variables are required for the base app.
# Add any future API keys or feature flags below.

# Example — if you add analytics in the future:
# VITE_ANALYTICS_ID=your_analytics_id_here

# Example — if you add a backend sync feature:
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://api.yourapp.com
